@*
    DESKTOP (lg+):
      - "Layla" fijo en la esquina superior-izquierda (dentro del sidebar)
      - Navbar siempre visible debajo

    MÓVIL (<lg):
      - Barra fija con "Layla" a la izquierda y botón hamburguesa a la derecha
      - Navbar desplegable al activar el checkbox

    NOTE: every NavLink carries data-enhance-nav="false". Without it Blazor's
    enhanced navigation intercepts the click, swaps the URL with pushState,
    fetches the new server-rendered HTML and tries to *patch* the existing
    DOM — but with InteractiveServer rendermode + streaming SSR the patch
    silently fails to apply, leaving the URL changed and the content stale.
    Forcing a full-page load per nav click sidesteps that interaction.
*@

<!-- ─── DESKTOP: bloque completo del sidebar ─── -->
<div class="
    hidden lg:flex lg:flex-col
    h-full w-full
    bg-linear-to-t from-base-purple-1 to-base-blue-3
    border-r border-white/10
">
    <!-- Brand / logo -->
    <div class="h-14 flex items-center px-5 border-b border-white/10 shrink-0">
        <a href="/home" data-enhance-nav="false"
           class="text-white font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors duration-200">
            Layla
        </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="flex-1 flex flex-col py-4 overflow-y-auto">
        <div class="px-4 pb-2">
            <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/30 font-semibold">Menu</span>
        </div>

        <div class="px-2 space-y-0.5">
            <div class="nav-item px-1">
                <NavLink href="/home" Match="NavLinkMatch.All" class="nav-link" data-enhance-nav="false">
                    <span class="bi bi-house-door-fill-nav-menu" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    Home
                </NavLink>
            </div>
            <div class="nav-item px-1">
                <NavLink href="/projects/my-projects" class="nav-link" data-enhance-nav="false">
                    <span class="bi bi-list-nested-nav-menu" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    My Projects
                </NavLink>
            </div>
            <div class="nav-item px-1">
                <NavLink href="/admin/dashboard" class="nav-link" data-enhance-nav="false">
                    <span class="bi bi-admin-nav-menu" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    Administration
                </NavLink>
            </div>
            <div class="nav-item px-1">
                <NavLink href="/admin/manage-users" class="nav-link" data-enhance-nav="false">
                    <span class="bi bi-admin-nav-menu" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    User Management
                </NavLink>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Version at bottom -->
        <div class="mt-auto px-5 py-4 border-t border-white/10">
            <span class="text-xs text-white/30">v1.0.0</span>
        </div>
    </nav>
</div>


<!-- ─── MOBILE: top bar + collapsible menu ─── -->
<div class="lg:hidden bg-linear-to-r from-base-blue-3 to-base-purple-1">

    <!-- Fixed bar: "Layla" left | hamburger right -->
    <div class="
        sticky top-0 z-50
        flex items-center justify-between
        px-5 h-14
        bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-md
        border-b border-white/10 sm:border-0
        shadow-[0_4px_24px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)]
    ">
        <a href="/home" data-enhance-nav="false"
           class="text-white font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors duration-200">
            Layla
        </a>

        <!-- Hamburger button — hidden checkbox label -->
        <label for="navbar-toggler"
               aria-label="Open navigation menu"
               class="cursor-pointer flex flex-col justify-center gap-1.5 p-2 rounded-md border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/10 active:scale-95 transition-all duration-200">
            <span class="block w-5 h-0.5 bg-white/80 rounded-full transition-transform duration-300 peer-checked:rotate-45 peer-checked:translate-y-2"></span>
            <span class="block w-5 h-0.5 bg-white/80 rounded-full transition-opacity duration-300 peer-checked:opacity-0"></span>
            <span class="block w-5 h-0.5 bg-white/80 rounded-full transition-transform duration-300 peer-checked:-rotate-45 peer-checked:-translate-y-2"></span>
        </label>
    </div>

    <!-- Hidden checkbox that controls the menu -->
    <input type="checkbox" id="navbar-toggler" class="peer hidden" />

    <!-- Dropdown menu -->
    <nav class="
        hidden peer-checked:flex flex-col
        py-3
        bg-black/70 backdrop-blur-md
        border-b border-white/10
        shadow-[0_8px_32px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]
        animate-[slideDown_0.2s_ease-out]
    ">
        <div class="px-4 pt-1 pb-2">
            <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/30 font-semibold">Menu</span>
        </div>

        <div class="px-2 space-y-0.5">
            <div class="nav-item px-1">
                <NavLink href="/home" Match="NavLinkMatch.All" class="nav-link" data-enhance-nav="false">
                    <span class="bi bi-house-door-fill-nav-menu" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    Home
                </NavLink>
            </div>
            <div class="nav-item px-1">
                <NavLink href="/projects/my-projects" class="nav-link" data-enhance-nav="false">
                    <span class="bi bi-list-nested-nav-menu" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    My Projects
                </NavLink>
            </div>
            <div class="nav-item px-1">
                <NavLink href="/admin/dashboard" class="nav-link" data-enhance-nav="false">
                    <span class="bi bi-admin-nav-menu" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    Administration
                </NavLink>
            </div>
            <div class="nav-item px-1">
                <NavLink href="/admin/manage-users" class="nav-link" data-enhance-nav="false">
                    <span class="bi bi-admin-nav-menu" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    User Management
                </NavLink>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

</div>
